00:37:01.580 --> 00:37:02.740
ng crossbow case.

00:37:05.060 --> 00:37:05.980
Pero kapag nakaya namin

00:37:05.980 --> 00:37:07.260
para mapaalis si Heneral Wei Yun,

00:37:07.740 --> 00:37:08.780
